Di Amcast Industrial Corp say di plan na to repurchase 500,000 share, or about 7% share outstanding, for open market matter.

Di iron product wey dem dey sell now, na 7.2 million common investment.

Amcast don first talk sey e go do repurchase but e no talk when or how many e wan buy back.

Dillon Read & Co na di exclusive agent for di stock buy back programme.

